Nicole
======

Requirements
------------

 * Python >= 2.5
 * Django >= 1.0 (python-django)
 * Markdown for Python >= 1.7 (python-markdown)
 * django-tagging >= 0.2.1 (python-django-tagging)

Installation
------------

 * Be sure to add a site to the database, and set SET_ID accordingly,
   (or the full url in the feeds will be jacked up).
 * You must add 'django.contrib.markup' to INSTALLED_APPS.
 * You must add 'tagging' to INSTALLED_APPS.
 * Make sure you install markdown for python (python-markdown).
